 Java Development Projects

A collection of Core Java and Advanced Java projects created to strengthen programming, object-oriented design, and software development skills.

 Topics Covered
- Core Java
- OOPs
- Collections Framework
- Exception Handling
- File Handling
- Multithreading
- JDBC
- Java 8 Features


 Projects Included

 Level 1 (Basic)

 1. CBSE Percentage Calculator
Calculates percentage from user-entered marks.

 2. Sum Three Numbers
Calculates the sum of three user-entered numbers.

 3. CGPA Calculator
Computes CGPA from marks or grades.

 4. Greeting User
Generates a personalized greeting message.

 5. Kilometer to Meter Converter
Converts distance from kilometers to meters.

 6. Integer Checker
Checks whether the entered value is an integer.


